headline: U.S. Bank Decreases Prime Lending Rate to 7.25 Percent
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, September 17, 2025--U.S. Bancorp (NYSE: USB) announced it has decreased its prime lending rate to 7.25 percent from 7.50 percent, effective tomorrow, September 18, 2025, at all U.S. Bank locations.
